item.title: Return of the Rebels
item.author: Priya Shah,
item.description: So last Thursday i had the good fortune to visit the Electric Brixton for the ‘Return of the Rebels’ tour. The set included Harlem based rappers Swave Sevah, Mazzi, Poison Pen and Dj Static, one of UK’s finest namely Lowkey, and the main event himself was Immortal Technique. Those who know who he is …
